summary: The 5 new enslaved wenches use the custom body/outfits of Yuriana's mod, also tweaked some dialogue options so wenches can use different ones from both mods.
descriptionHtml:
[color=#CCFB5D][size=6][center]INFO:[/center][/size][/color][center][img]https://i.imgur.com/sX79SG9.jpg[/img]

[size=4]Made a patch so the 5 new wenches of immersive wenches use the custom body/outfits of Yuriana's mod, also tweaked some dialogue options so this kind of "merges" some features from both mods (dialogues and custom armors).
[/size][/center]
[center]
[size=4][size=4]The patch requires KS hairs mod and obviously immersive wenches and Yuriana's mod, at first I thought on making the hairs standalone but if you use KS or the KS&SG hairs patch already its better just to use them.

[color=#CCFB5D][size=6][center][u]Requirements:[/u][/center][/size][/color]-[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68311]KS Hairdos[/url]﻿
-[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51189/]Immersive Wenches[/url]﻿
-[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/77903/?]Buxom Wench Yuriana[/url]﻿
[/size]
I made this since several people requested the wenches from Immersive Wenches to have standalone bodies. While testing I saw that making the wenches use their own bodies make them a little more "unique", for now I will see how it goes with at least making the 5 new wenches I added in the last update use the wench body since making every wench in the mod use standalone bodies its a little insane because of the different hair versions and compatibility with the wench expansions. So I will try to improve this bit by bit eventually.
[/size]
[size=4]
